# Cloudflare Pages routing. The app lives at /app; oignon.dev root is the
# landing page.
#
# Share links (/g/<code>) are handled by the Pages Function functions/g/[code].js,
# NOT a rule here: a `/g/* /app/index.html 200` rewrite was silently shadowed by
# Cloudflare's SPA fallback (it served the root landing page at /g/<code>).
# Functions have deterministic precedence, so routing lives there instead.
#
# No active rules currently. Keep this file for documentation and future rules.
